| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4866 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7c38fe22-8b1a-55e0-8403-f2c65c3839d7"
